Paper: hep-th/9510166

Date: 1995-10-23

Title: The Classical $r$-Matrix for the Relativistic Ruijsenaars-Schneider

SystemAuthors: Jean Avan and Genevieve Rollet

Comments: LaTeX file, no figures, 8 pages

We compute the classical $r$-matrix for the relativistic generalization ofthe Calogero-Moser model, or Ruijsenaars-Schneider model, at all values of thespeed-of-light parameter $\lambda$. We connect it with the non-relativisticCalogero-Moser $r$-matrix $(\lambda \rightarrow -1)$ and the $\lambda = 1$sine-Gordon soliton limit.